               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Māryām "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 3ra-84vb)&#xD; I-1) Maṣḥafa
                     śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 3ra-9ra)&#xD; I-2)
                     Introductory exhortation (fols. 9ra-11rb)&#xD; I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki
                     wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... "I worship Thee..." (fols. 11rb-12va)&#xD; I-4) Taʾammǝra
                     Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 44 miracles (fols. 13ra-84vb).&#xD; I-5) ʾAkkonu
                     bǝʾsi ... "Does not the man ...": 29 strophes (distributed among the miracles
                     of Mary, fols. 15va-64rb)&#xD; II) Taʾammǝra Gabra Manfas Qǝddus "Miracles of
                     Gabra Manfas Qǝddus": 2 miracles (fols. 85ra-67ra)&#xD; III) Taʾammǝra Mikāʾel
                     "Miracles of Michael": 2 miracles (fols. 87ra-88vb)&#xD; IV) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus
                     "Miracles of Jesus": 5 miracles (fol. 88vb-94vb)&#xD; &#xD; Additiones 1-3;
                     colophon.</summary>
